makes me doubt my own thoughts.

239
00:16:26,640 --> 00:16:30,210
Once I was shaken, you
infiltrated my mind,

240
00:16:30,244 --> 00:16:31,679
waiting for this
slightest flutter

241
00:16:31,712 --> 00:16:35,217
to anticipate my actions,
seeking out any hints

242
00:16:35,251 --> 00:16:37,887
to my next move.

243
00:16:37,920 --> 00:16:41,491
All you're doing is
copying me like a monkey.

244
00:16:41,524 --> 00:16:44,128
You can beat me
with cheap tricks.

245
00:16:44,162 --> 00:16:46,531
I'll crush you.

246
00:16:46,565 --> 00:16:48,367
When I'm finished
with you, you'll

247
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:50,736
never open that
monkey mouth again.

248
00:16:50,770 --> 00:16:55,842
You time it precisely,
waiting for the right moment.

249
00:16:55,876 --> 00:16:56,878
-What is that?

250
00:16:56,911 --> 00:16:58,913
-The instant my mind
because unfocused,

251
00:16:58,946 --> 00:17:02,117
you create a new illusion.

252
00:17:02,150 --> 00:17:04,253
With your hypnotic
eye, you induce

253
00:17:04,287 --> 00:17:07,958
me to make hand signs while
you are making the same signs.

254
00:17:07,992 --> 00:17:10,995
So you seem to be copying
me when actually you're

255
00:17:11,029 --> 00:17:12,764
controlling my movements.

256
00:17:12,798 --> 00:17:13,932
-Water-style.

257
00:17:13,965 --> 00:17:15,401
Giant vortex jutsu.

258
00:17:25,046 --> 00:17:25,614
-Impossible.

259
00:17:30,420 --> 00:17:31,855
Now, that I know this.

260
00:17:31,888 --> 00:17:34,791
A very simple plan
can defeat you.

261
00:17:34,825 --> 00:17:38,863
First, neutralize your piercing
eye with zero visibility mist.

262
00:17:41,967 --> 00:17:46,106
KAKASHI (VOICEOVER): The mist
is slowing my reaction time.

263
00:17:46,140 --> 00:17:50,711
-Next, neutralize your hypnotic
eye by keeping my own eyes

264
00:17:50,745 --> 00:17:52,080
closed.

265
00:17:52,113 --> 00:17:56,318
You can't bore into my mind if
you can't look into my eyes.

266
00:17:56,352 --> 00:17:59,322
-Brilliant, except
with your eyes closed,

267
00:17:59,356 --> 00:18:01,359
you can't see me either.

268
00:18:01,392 --> 00:18:03,662
-Have you forgotten
who I am, Kakashi?

269
00:18:03,695 --> 00:18:05,597
I'm the demon of
the hidden mist,

270
00:18:05,630 --> 00:18:07,532
master of the silent kill.

271
00:18:07,567 --> 00:18:09,569
I can take you our
by sound alone.

272
00:18:17,679 --> 00:18:19,915
SHADOW CLONE (VOICEOVER):
He read my movements,

273
00:18:19,948 --> 00:18:22,819
but that's not possible.

274
00:18:22,852 --> 00:18:25,522
-I was so close, but I
couldn't quite get to him.

275
00:18:25,555 --> 00:18:28,659
-Naruto, can you do it again?

276
00:18:28,693 --> 00:18:29,160
-Huh?

277
00:18:29,194 --> 00:18:30,028
Of course.

278
00:18:30,061 --> 00:18:30,762
Nothing can stop me.

279
00:18:30,796 --> 00:18:31,897
Believe it.

280
00:18:31,930 --> 00:18:34,000
SASUKE (VOICEOVER): He
doesn't want to show it,

281
00:18:34,033 --> 00:18:35,468
but he's exhausted.

282
00:18:35,502 --> 00:18:38,972
The shadow clone jutsu
uses up so much chakra.

283
00:18:39,006 --> 00:18:42,276
But thanks to him,
I figured it out.

284
00:18:42,310 --> 00:18:45,047
I know how to break through.

285
00:18:45,080 --> 00:18:47,350
SHADOW CLONE (VOICEOVER):
The human eye cannot track

286
00:18:47,383 --> 00:18:49,385
my movements.

287
00:18:49,419 --> 00:18:50,854
It must have been a coincidence.

288
00:18:56,661 --> 00:18:58,497
-Naruto, run for it!

289
00:18:58,531 --> 00:19:00,466
Get out of here and
attack from the outside.

290
00:19:00,499 --> 00:19:02,335
Hurry!

291
00:19:02,368 --> 00:19:03,036
-Uh.

292
00:19:03,069 --> 00:19:03,570
All right.

293
00:19:03,603 --> 00:19:05,572
You got it.

294
00:19:05,605 --> 00:19:06,974
-You cannot escape.

295
00:19:19,323 --> 00:19:20,892
-You think you can keep me here?

296
00:19:20,925 --> 00:19:24,263
Forget it.

297
00:19:24,296 --> 00:19:24,997
-That's it.

298
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:26,231
Fire-style.

299
00:19:26,265 --> 00:19:27,233
Fireball jutsu!

300
00:19:53,500 --> 00:19:56,136
-I couldn't get passed him.

301
00:19:56,169 --> 00:19:57,538
-That was good, Naruto.

302
00:19:57,571 --> 00:19:59,540
-Huh?

303
00:19:59,573 --> 00:20:01,510
One more time?

304
00:20:01,543 --> 00:20:02,244
-Yeah.

305
00:20:02,277 --> 00:20:02,945
Let's do it.

306
00:20:06,549 --> 00:20:09,353
SASUKE (VOICEOVER): There must
be a limit to his chakra, too.

307
00:20:09,386 --> 00:20:10,988
I can feel him slowing down.

308
00:20:18,865 --> 00:20:20,634
SHADOW CLONE (VOICEOVER):
No more games.

309
00:20:20,667 --> 00:20:22,903
I need to stop this now.

310
00:20:22,937 --> 00:20:24,371
This time you'll stay down.

311
00:20:30,212 --> 00:20:30,746
-Sasuke!

312
00:20:36,186 --> 00:20:41,693
KAKASHI (VOICEOVER): An enemy
you can't see and can't hear.

313
00:20:41,726 --> 00:20:45,498
It's been a long time since
I faced anyone this tough.

314
00:20:45,531 --> 00:20:50,705
And Sasuke and Naruto, I don't
know if they can hold out.

315
00:20:53,508 --> 00:20:55,377
Stay calm.

316
00:20:55,410 --> 00:20:56,579
Think.

317
00:20:56,612 --> 00:21:00,384
Where will he strike?

318
00:21:00,417 --> 00:21:01,351
The bridge builder.

319
00:21:18,472 --> 00:21:19,374
-Too late.

320
00:21:22,712 --> 00:21:25,215
[screaming]

321
00:21:35,394 --> 00:21:38,798
[music playing]

322
00:23:10,647 --> 00:23:13,184
NARUTO: Why did it
turn out this way?

323
00:23:13,217 --> 00:23:15,987
How could this have happened?

324
00:23:16,020 --> 00:23:18,690
I never asked for
your protection.

325
00:23:18,724 --> 00:23:21,761
I didn't need you
to do what you did.

326
00:23:21,794 --> 00:23:23,396
I hated you.

327
00:23:23,429 --> 00:23:27,034
Yet, you sacrificed
your life for mine.

328
00:23:27,068 --> 00:23:28,218
I'll never forgive you.

329
00:23:31,251 --> 00:23:34,885
Next time, "The Broken Seal."

